Actions
SQL Server standalone servers (SQL Server and Analysis Services) 

Check the database status (online, offline, recovery) 



use master
go   
select serverproperty ('servername') as [Instance Name],
name as [Database Name],state_desc as [Status] ,user_access_desc as [User Access Desc],
case is_auto_close_on
when 1 then 'ON'
when 0 then 'OFF'
end as [Auto Close]
from sys.databases
Check the active connection. Advise Service Assurance to reconfirm the application services stop.



SELECT 
    DB_NAME(dbid) as DBName, hostname,
    COUNT(dbid) as NumberOfConnections,
    loginame as LoginName
FROM
    master..sysprocesses
WHERE 
    dbid > 0
GROUP BY 
    dbid, loginame,hostname
go
